#. module: website_sale_penguin
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:website_sale_penguin.penguin_product
msgid ""
"<b>Chest contour.</b> Measure around the widest point of the chest,keeping "
"the tape horizontal."
msgstr ""
"<b>Brustumfang.</b> Messe den breitesten Punkt der Brust und halte das "
"Massband horizontal."

#. module: website_sale_penguin
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:website_sale_penguin.penguin_product
msgid ""
"<b>Hip contour.</b> Keeping the feet together, measure around the widest "
"point of the hip, keeping the tape horizontal."
msgstr ""
"<b>Taillenumfang.</b> Messe um den engsten Punkt der Taille, halte das "
"Massband horizontal."

#. module: website_sale_penguin
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:website_sale_penguin.penguin_product
msgid ""
"<b>Waist contour.</b> Measure around the narrowest point of the waist, "
"keeping the tape horizontal."
msgstr ""
"<b>Hüftumfang.</b> Halte die Füsse zusammen und messe um den breitesten "
"Punkt der Hüfte, halte das Massband horizontal."

